beer.beer_description:
A collab born from many rounds on the course and back at the bar, we’re stoked to be linking up with our Byron Bay-based golf mates Birds of Condor on the release of Swing Juice Country Club XPA! 

Coming in at a very sessionalbe 4% ABV, this XPA is bursting with notes of citrus and pine, thanks to the generous but balanced dry hop utilising both Aussie and American hops. Crisp on the palate, but still sporting a firm malt body and approachable bitterness, Swing Juice really is a HOLE - IN - ONE!
